{"tid":2186571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日媒指一名日籍記者疑被本港警方拘捕","createTime":"2020-09-03T05:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T07:11:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"566db13e2aba51553d4c8fb7e1c885c2f047d205","tid":2186571,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"日本《產經新聞》報道，一名日籍自由記者，懷疑被本港警方拘捕，日本駐港總領事館正在確認消息。 報道指，這名男子在2016年來自一直在香港居住，去年起持續拍攝反修例示威，個人社交網站最後一篇帖文在星期一發出，當晚在太子及旺角等多處，有人就港鐵太子站831事件發生一年聚集，警方拘捕共16人，分別涉嫌非法集結、公眾地方擾亂秩序、襲警及管有仿製火器等。"},{"pid":"58d3be0748c3674bdc24dc948bd04e486e2ac603","tid":2186571,"uid":224533,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ByuDDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ByuDDW.jpg&h=c3ec7f20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f96d7875e3f211255a1413557c7de090d36d06","tid":2186571,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同埋身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"bc428c82c91da783e1f7e4c7646c5f49dda0c9ae","tid":2186571,"uid":282930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"之前支那就話唔好搞周庭bb怕日本人反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家班皇軍又同你倒米，刁總我係你就唔忍啦"},{"pid":"8b09f7b68ddf65fd37719bcba8e29152d6afde2f","tid":2186571,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.